data.description: This beautiful, well-maintained home is new to the market!  With over 3700 square feet total and sitting on just over 25 acres with a 30x40 shop the privacy and the serenity will not disappoint! This is a home you must see in person and possession is offered at closing! This home features a new roof, with 3 bedrooms and 3 baths, a newly renovated kitchen with so much cabinetry, as well as bathrooms with custom vanities and a new jetted master tub, the real wood floors make this house a home. Call today to schedule your personal showing.
